ADV7511 support I2S or SPDIF as audio input interfaces. This commit
enable support for SPDIF.

Signed-off-by: Bogdan Togorean <bogdan.togorean@analog.com>
Reviewed-by: Andrzej Hajda <a.hajda@samsung.com>
---
